data.description: Welcome to this lovely 2 family home located in close proximity to all major transportation. This home features 2 units in which each unit having  3 bedrooms, 1 bath, open livingroom -kitchen concept. The basement is finished with full bath and kitchenette for extra entertaining space or think outside the box living. YES THERE IS PARKING. Parking is located in the back, entrance is between 34 and 36 Dodd st. This is a great opportunity for first time investors or first time home buyers to live in one unit and rent the other. Prime location, easy commute to and from NYC. HIGHEST AND BEST SUNDAY 7PM
